smtp (simple mail transfer protocol) tcp port no:25
nmap -sV -O <ip>
to get the banner of smtp
nc <ip/domain> 25
vrfy admin@<servername> to verify admin is there or not after you get a netcat
use auxiliary/scanner/smtp/smtp_enum

telnet demo.ine.local 25
HELO attacker.xyz
mail from: admin@attacker.xyz
rcpt to:root@openmailbox.xyz
data
Subject: Hi Root
Hello,
This is a fake mail sent using telnet command.
From,
Admin
.
Note: There is a dot(.) in the last line which indicates the termination of data.
